1) Data Binding :- Sharing data inside a component

  i)one way Binding
   html -> ts  OR ts-> html
   ts:- component
   html:- view

   a)1.1 :- component -> view [ts -> html]

    i)  string interpolation - {{expression}}
    ii) property binding - [attribute] = "property"

   b)1.2 :- view -> component [html -> ts]

    i) Event binding - (event name) = "function name()"
    ii)Event binding using ($event) - (event name)= "function name()"



Angular Routing:- to set a path for a component

{
  path:value, component: component class name
}


Angular directives:- to manipulate DOM elements

1) Component directives

2) Structural directives
  i) ngFor

Angular Forms:-

1) Template driven Forms( first html design):- used for html page designing
2) Model driven forms( first ts file -> html design) :- used for advanced  validation methods
  i)Reactive Forms Module :- [form group,array,control]
   - we can directly add vallidation methods
   - -> Add validation
     -> import Reactive forms modules

